title: How to Take Whatever Life Throws At You
itunes:title: How to Take Whatever Life Throws At You
description:
Episode 301 -  Life can be brutal sometimes. What are you doing in the calm moments to prepare yourself for the battles that life throws at you? You must realize that the better you are, the easier life will be. No matter how hard it gets.
